{"tid":2254061,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"買左12Pro嘅人恭喜曬","createTime":"2020-10-22T14:20:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T14:32:44.000Z","uid":235631,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fece529df2d89095a4cdeb9ba25ae86415cf2237","tid":2254061,"uid":235631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:20:38.000Z","msg":"你買咗部更加重、聚手、容易刮花嘅iPhone 12 but 恭喜你獲得 LIDAR x 1 LENS x1 2G RAM <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6OVTfTS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6OVTfTS.jpg&h=af983e66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n其實佢出嗰陣我睇個spec已經知佢模一樣 <br />\n<br />\n你買Pro Max 都好 因為起碼佢相機好啲 <br />\n<br />\nQ:*你呀2 GB ram長用好重要喎<br />\n<br />\nA: 其實 iPad Air 都係4G, 我相信iOS 4GB ram已經夠用、足以應付四年、四年後部機已經88<br />\n<br />\nQ: Lider好重要 <br />\n<br />\nA:其實iphone x已經有LIder 佢叫face ID 佢可以幫你解鎖iphone、已曾經為香港出去創科比賽嘅人嚟講、我覺得除非你好鍾意影相、A14算法已經解決到、做工程係會用尺、因為佢都係有誤差<br />\n<br />\nQ長鏡頭好重要<br />\n<br />\nA:係呀啱變態佬、3x? 你唔記得你係人、你識行？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最重要要講三次 Pro 係同大陸同版本、唔知佢啲（精）片有冇錦上添花 香港買嘅12係國際版"},{"pid":"f84d9fdae0b83cdc4b0aa2ac52fbfb641c4ef961","tid":2254061,"uid":36296,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:24:18.000Z","msg":"Lider or LiDAR?"},{"pid":"1e2674e3dabd54c8509b69a7c44c51e782ecd8d9","tid":2254061,"uid":235631,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f84d9fdae0b83cdc4b0aa2ac52fbfb641c4ef961","tid":2254061,"uid":36296,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:24:18.000Z","msg":"Lider or LiDAR?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:25:12.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"b2da60857162d3a6a143736d74c20383e313ea65","tid":2254061,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:28:01.000Z","msg":"大家唔洗理佢<br />\n一定係買PRO"},{"pid":"36c6f0e4845976f2d80564bad899b2515214b98f","tid":2254061,"uid":3122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b2da60857162d3a6a143736d74c20383e313ea65","tid":2254061,"uid":3122,"l